author: cschoett
msg: Another sample for the WSC, this sample includes a simple AXIS webservice, which is used to generate a WSC and build a small client web app.  The WSC is accessed through a JSP file which makes multiple calls to the webservice using the WSC.
Currently won't build until new wsc build macro gets added to beehive-tools.xml (coming soon).
